>\n指示班垃圾老散hea做收隊的高層一定係知情者,<strong>係姦殺異見人士的一連串行動中有份</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>只要拉當日到場的散仔去新屋嶺嚴刑拷問就一定查到黑手</ins><br />\n狗隊根本無得賴唔知同無做過"},{"pid":"622896e4aa01f52d70e074cfb99615cbd53f4140","tid":1829911,"uid":19634,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"警渣做任何事都唔會驚，因為一定無後果，全部有權既人渣都企曬佢哋個邊，香港人究竟下定決心攬炒未？攬炒香港經濟一定對大陸有影響㗎，大陸而家仲不斷靠香港瘋狂cap水"},{"pid":"c36eed8e2f04ea37815ae32a7fce9afca0a7e48e","tid":1829911,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"731cc485e5b5058ad2a659faba3df8af74ff8da9","tid":1829911,"uid":65887,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"上次果單又係不了了之<br />\n呢啲野好心就高調啲搞, 記者日日跟進<br />\n如果唔係只會不斷發生"},{"pid":"8021e63d5ac15777c6dc68da255f646375840f1e","tid":1829911,"uid":286966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04fe7c5c200c8d65e1bc20d49fa54f9336312ac","tid":1829911,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab174de8fe2dc6e147471fc0aad6158370bf9cd","tid":1829911,"uid":62192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"記恊應該差唔多發聲明表明話對事件予以強烈譴責"},{"pid":"d84aef4d6b965360cbac75d8aba495d8d8aee947","tid":1829911,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"死性不改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5223f0eb64b52f437b4240147eb173dc9dec04b5","tid":1829911,"uid":47558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead